snippet.title: Painkiller Resurrection PC video game trailer
snippet.description:
http://gamezplay.org - The latest sequel to the successful Painkiller series .
The game will hit stores on October 27th: Get ready to take on Purgatory (and the various creatures inhabiting it) as you take on the role of ëWild Billí Sherman who gets drawn into the endless War between Heaven and Hello a devilishly hot hell-ride of a game!
